'''The Myth and Fantasy Calendar 1974''' was published by [[Faun Fantasy Press]] and created by [[Jonathan T. Hodge]]. Illustrations were done by  nine different artists, including [[Tim Kirk]]. The calendar was produced in a limited edition run of 1,000 copies.

* Dimension: 11 1/4 x 8 1/2 inches
* Stapled on the fold
* Punched hanging hole
